data.description:
MOVE IN READY!! 
Welcome to this stunning, just eight months young home, nestled in a delightful community! Revel in the expansive, well-lit living area that seamlessly blends with the dining and kitchen areas.  The modern kitchen features stainless steel appliances, convenient roll-out shelves, and exquisite quartz countertops. The lovely dining space offers views of the charming backyard, while the kitchen island provides additional bar seating. Upstairs, discover three spacious bedrooms, a generously sized primary walk-in closet, laundry facilities, and an additional storage closet. The upgrade from carpet to luxury vinyl plank flooring adds a touch of modern elegance. This home is brimming with features and eagerly awaits its new owner! To convey: washer and dryer, refrigerator, outdoor garden beds, pergola, Murphy bed, all window treatments, and the security system with front and back RING SYSTEM and floodlight camera.
